title: Uber settles with Waymo
text:
Uber settles with Waymo 1:38pm EST - 01:09 
Alphabet's self-driving car unit settled its trade secrets dispute with the ride-hailing firm, Uber. As Fred Katayama reports, Uber promised not to use Waymo's technology in its autonomous vehicles. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
